
@{
ViewBag.Title = "TeamMessage";
}

<h2>Team Messages</h2>
<hr />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h3>Current Thread</h3>
        <ul class="list-group">
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <strong>
                    What are the ways we can improve revenue and reach our goal this month?
                </strong>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    I think it really comes down to being more efficient in our sales calls. We need to figure
                    out a way to call smarter. It would help to call only those who are home instead of a random
                    phone number.
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-10"><em>James Sparrow</em></div>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    I agree. I wish there was a way to track that.
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-10"><em>Jimmy Sparrow</em></div>
            </li>
            <li class="list-group-item">
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    Maybe Conner could create a automated tool that analyzes our calls and automatically
                    generates a calling report. That would save a lot of time and make our time better spent.
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-offset-10"><em>Jack Sparrow</em></div>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="comment">Comment:</label>
                <textarea class="form-control" id="comment" rows="5" placeholder="Insert comment here"></textarea>
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Comment</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<hr />
<div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
        <h3>Start New Thread</h3>
        <form>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="comment"></label>
                <input class="form-control" id="question" placeholder="Insert question here">
            </div>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

